
            Video
            The actress who almost died from undetected heart condition
            Actress Rebecca Shorrocks nearly lost her life to cardiomyopathy - a heart condition she never knew she had. According to the charity, Cardiac Risk in the Young, 12 young people lose their lives every week as a result of undiagnosed heart conditions.Now Ms Shorrocks wants to push for mandatory screening on the NHS for everyone over the age of 14.Video Journalist: Gem O'Reilly
                
                        18 Nov 2018
                    
                
        
